title: It’s Not Too Late to Get Into ‘Peaky Blinders’ | The Watch
description:
Season 5 of ‘Peaky Blinders’ premieres on Netflix tomorrow, but it’s not too late to get into the show (2:00). We talk about the surprisingly stacked cast (9:36), our favorite characters on the show (27:05), and what else we’re watching on TV right now (29:58).

Host: Chris Ryan
Guest: Juliet Litman
